 </i18n-message></h2>
<p>Works natively with Cisco Outbound Dialer and Cisco Contact Center platforms (UCCE, PCCE, UCCX), enabling centralized campaign management and leveraging existing call routing, agent desktops, and reporting systems.</p>
<p>You can create multiple campaigns, each linked to a separate Cisco Campaign.</p>
<h3 id="Call-Routing-(Direct-agent,-Shared,-Hybrid)"><span id="OutboundCampaigns-CallRouting(Direct-agent,Shared,Hybrid)"></span>Call Routing (Direct-agent, Shared, Hybrid)
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.10/outbound-campaigns#Call-Routing-(Direct-agent,-Shared,-Hybrid)">
