   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h4>
<p>For a multilayered outbound approach with Cisco, consider using Cisco Personal Callback where the outbound contact is first targeted to a specified Cisco Contact Center Agent. If the agent is not available, route the outbound contact to a fallback queue or choose an alternate digital channel to reach out to the customer.</p>
